WEBVTT

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:28.920
Sir

00:01:03.360 --> 00:01:03.680
Sir.

00:01:04.360 --> 00:01:05.519
This man's pulse is weak,

00:01:05.519 --> 00:01:06.560
he's lost too much blood,

00:01:06.560 --> 00:01:07.960
and his internal organs are damaged.

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:09.080
If this continues,

00:01:09.800 --> 00:01:11.860
I'm afraid I won't be able to save him.

00:01:12.440 --> 00:01:13.520
He cannot die.

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:17.760
I'm missing some medicines from my kit.

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:18.690
I'll go get them.

00:01:19.080 --> 00:01:20.080
Hurry back.

00:01:46.280 --> 00:01:47.560
Isn't this Clerk Li?

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:50.650
