00:03:06.320 --> 00:03:08.520
I'll need your guidance and support.

00:03:09.440 --> 00:03:10.200
Of course.

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:15.320
Hurry up.

00:03:20.520 --> 00:03:21.250
Move faster.

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:22.640
Hurry.

