00:03:29.079 --> 00:03:30.680
I'll wash the dirty clothes.

00:03:30.760 --> 00:03:32.290
I'll treat you to tea later.

00:03:32.320 --> 00:03:33.079
Tea! Tea!

00:03:34.720 --> 00:03:35.920
